				<dd>2025-서울관악-1441</dd>
			</dl>
			<p class="text-[13px] text-[#aaaaaa]">
				Built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#666666] hover:underline">Astro</a> · Hosted on GitHub Pages
			</p>
		</div>
